cubecraft
=========

Lightweight mock package that wraps the provided IFU spectral cube generator.

Quick start
-----------

1. Install from source (in project root):

   python -m pip install -e .

2. Use the generator API:

   from cubecraft import generator
   ds = generator.ResolvedSpectralCubeDataset(n_cubes=1, n_gals=1, init_grid_size=17, final_grid_size=21, n_spectral_slices=2, verbose=False)
   cube, params = ds[0]

Notes
-----
This package contains a fairly heavy scientific dependency stack (astropy, scipy, torch). The initial commit keeps the original algorithm intact and exposes it as a module.
